<HEADLINE>
LAPD STEPS UP MANHUNT IN GONZALEZ SLAYING
</HEADLINE>
 (For use by NYTimes News Service clients) 
By LISA VAN PROYEN, ALEXA HAUSSLER AND JASON KANDEL 
c.2000 Los Angeles Daily News  
