not completely sure of its demise. That's because, hey, everybody
else might like it. Look how long ``Veronica's Closet'' stunk
around. A hit, no matter how horrible, remains a hit. Nobody
cancels shows in Hollywood just because they're bad. But a really
solid case can be made that ``Clerks,'' the new animated series
