   LANDSCAPE-STONE _ Nothing says permanent, substantial and
dependable like stone, so it's no wonder that people seeking to
shape the landscapes around their homes often turn to natural or
manufactured stone. Local landscape designers and home improvement
materials suppliers say various kinds of landscape timbers are
still in use, but stackable concrete blocks have become the first
choice where walls are needed to hold and shape the earth. (Dayton
Daily News). 40. WITH PHOTOS.
