</P>
<P>
   ``He's one of these absent-minded-professor types.'' She also
noted, however, that her son, whom she teaches at home through the
Tri-City Homeschoolers program, has ``worked really hard for it (a
victory) for so many years.''
</P>
<P>
   The spelling bee, sponsored by E.W. Scripps Co., offers the
winner prizes that include $10,000.
</P>
