<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-05-31 15:11 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A0755 &Cx1f; tdt-z
u k BC-NOLAN-COLUMN-BOS &LR;      05-31 0696
