<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-ENIGMA-$ADV04-COX </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    BRITISH UNHAPPY OVER US THEFT OF 'THEIR' WAR STORY; WHAT OF
POLES?
