home.us.net/(tilde)encore/Enigma/enigma.html
</P>
<P>
   Enigma ciphering:
hops.cs.jhu.edu/(tilde)russell/classes/enigma/enigma.html
</P>
<P>
   Jeff Nesmith's email address is jeffn(at)coxnews.com.
</P>
<P>
   Bartosz Weglarczyk's email address is bartoszw(at)coxnews
</P>
<P>
   ENDIT
</P>
