<HEADLINE>
EARTHBOUND KITE IS A SOARING LEGACY
</HEADLINE>
 (For use by NYTimes News Service clients) 
By MARY ROGERS 
c.2000 Fort Worth Star-Telegram 
<TEXT>
<P>
   FORT WORTH, Texas _ Manny Estrada made his way happily through
