</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-ELIMINATE-BUSH-NYT </SLUG>
  
<TEXT>
<P>
   EDITORS:
</P>
<P>
   BUSH (Albuquerque) will not move in tonight's New York Times
News Service file.
</P>
<P>
   N.Y. Times News Service, May 31.
</P>
</TEXT>
</BODY>
<TRAILER>
NYT-05-31-00 1914EDT &QL; 
