<P>
   ALL BUDGETED STORIES HAVE MOVED except: BIZGLANCE,
CAMPAIGN-BRIEFS, WORLD-BRIEFS, BKN-ARATON-COLUMN,
BKN-KNICKS-PACERS, BBA-YANKS-OAKLAND, BBN-METS-DODGERS and
GLF-GOLF-CARTS.
