</P>
<P>
   FLA-TOBACCO-SUIT (Miami)
</P>
<P>
   KMART-APPOINT (Undated)
</P>
<P>
   CNN-ANNIVERSARY (Atlanta)
</P>
<P>
   BUSH (Albuquerque)
</P>
<P>
   N.Y. Times News Service.
</P>
</TEXT>
</BODY>
